Class Game

java.lang.Object
com.example.miniproyecto1.model.juego.Game
public class Game extends Object
Represents the core logic of the game. This class manages the gameâ€™s state and ties together the user interface (labels, text field, progress bar) with the game logic (Timer, Word, Level). It acts as the "model" in an MVC pattern, while GameController acts as the controller.
